{"tid":416331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過令你覺得恐懼嘅鬼壓床","createTime":"2017-09-27T16:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T19:18:06.000Z","uid":75320,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccc9b8ca232e7f05ea67aab92c27258d1707259","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知 鬼壓床只係睡眠麻痺 個人一攰就好易出現 都有啲方法可以去試到<br />\n我曾經主動試到過幾次 感覺都唔會話好驚<br />\n<br />\n但有時夜晚訓教 個感覺好強烈 真係覺得側面好似有啲野 除左個頭全身都郁唔到 但會恐懼到唔敢望去第二度<br />\n<br />\n會唔會真係有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0648f30e37ea7ac2f1ff09d7ddb8402002164ef","tid":416331,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb2d9328dad6e6526c5a5a151be6e6ec674ac70f","tid":416331,"uid":33312,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:48:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有一排我成日出現呢種情況，初初好驚<br />\n之後有幾次中午訓個時又出現過，出現呢種情況個時，大腦仲諗到野，我就心諗，窗邊咁大太陽我就唔信咁邪，之後就同佢鬥力，慢慢手指可以自由活動，但手腕就郁唔到，但之後好攰<br />\n<br />\n所以而家每次出現呢種情況,都係唔理佢合埋眼，繼續訓"},{"pid":"9a7808501ca4cf03b47fc6324472afc0477b1fff","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，有一排我成日出現呢種情況，初初好驚<br />\n之後有幾次中午訓個時又出現過，出現呢種情況個時，大腦仲諗到野，我就心諗，窗邊咁大太陽我就唔信咁邪，之後就同佢鬥力，慢慢手指可以自由活動，但手腕就郁唔到，但之後好攰<br />\n<br />\n所以而家每次出現呢種情況,都係唔理佢合埋眼，繼續訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你下次試下唔好爭扎 慢慢你會聽到收音機沙沙聲<br />\n人地話個聲冇左之後可在靈魂出竅<br />\n<br />\n利申 而家返工冇晏晝可以試 夜晚又恐怖"},{"pid":"d3b5ea3b5c15a810cf08f917dbcd418517ffb602","tid":416331,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"試過幾次，合埋眼放鬆身體過一陣就無事"},{"pid":"299660775af6309cf35be89a87056b4696a00178","tid":416331,"uid":43563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"以前成日都有，有幾次係連抖氣都抖唔到"},{"pid":"00b20d6aa03a613ba91e2724be4a583aa4393d65","tid":416331,"uid":140968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"攰嗰陣試下個身擺直但個頭向左或者右擺，咁樣瞓好容易會有鬼壓床<br />\n利申：個人經驗，有fd都話咁樣特別易有"},{"pid":"103fe13a592b3b885bfd68a9ee009842aec4f197","tid":416331,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"屌我好想試"},{"pid":"041bc97ee36d89948cb3bde85d38e526dff4e08d","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過幾次，合埋眼放鬆身體過一陣就無事</blockquote><br />\n我以前係咁 都覺得冇乜野<br />\n但最近果啲完全唔同feel 成個感覺好強烈"},{"pid":"d7dd2ef93893f15b150d54438bc7fbbfc6d6b8e0","tid":416331,"uid":140968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我好想試</blockquote><br />\n試下打側個頭咁樣瞓"},{"pid":"ac4fd3db615a04d33e810c37a0e1b659d9ac9779","tid":416331,"uid":3852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"有次見到細細地、起晒尖角好似刺蝟咁嘅球體凌空飄浮緊好快閃走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bebe9b48129a7aa108e6441b8658da49ed814c6","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前成日都有，有幾次係連抖氣都抖唔到</blockquote><br />\n巴打睡眠窒息？<br />\n利申 鳩嗡"},{"pid":"88b60d5a8087e146d7913d3d41e4e1cc79c2acca","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌我好想試</blockquote><br />\n試下打側個頭咁樣瞓</blockquote><br />\n有人教過 <br />\n要將自己身體整到好攰<br />\n訓前再不停催眠自己要有意識咁訓<br />\n我真係試到過"},{"pid":"b093cda0b9a11b598ac0f6546fc2d13ebd2f3fb8","tid":416331,"uid":140968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前成日都有，有幾次係連抖氣都抖唔到</blockquote><br />\n巴打睡眠窒息？<br />\n利申 鳩嗡</blockquote><br />\n我都試過鬼壓床+抖唔到氣，嗰陣好驚"},{"pid":"4eae50f3b8e667250a1f3084ed98893596bae521","tid":416331,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"我成日都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔會恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道嚟之前嘅徵兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼壓床完之後<br />\n有一半機率會知道自己嗰一陣發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a58476771d5fd90c95250735a601d1cdfb7c3dc","tid":416331,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"另外有次打側瞓出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到背脊後面有嘢好似想潛入我身體度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fde05be1330549d640a49c7a2b653a1baac383","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次見到細細地、起晒尖角好似刺蝟咁嘅球體凌空飄浮緊好快閃走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打出左竅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0337090fed0c07d2758e62a3aab1d7922f17d517","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外有次打側瞓出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到背脊後面有嘢好似想潛入我身體度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf50d292e2de56ab5d72455d646b010765d76a4","tid":416331,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有次見到細細地、起晒尖角好似刺蝟咁嘅球體凌空飄浮緊好快閃走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打出左竅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇 仲係肉體到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 張開雙眼望上天花板望到啲不明物體嚇到我合返埋眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575b66543165c5f816e850b91fcdaa69681f5527","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有次見到細細地、起晒尖角好似刺蝟咁嘅球體凌空飄浮緊好快閃走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打出左竅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇 仲係肉體到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 張開雙眼望上天花板望到啲不明物體嚇到我合返埋眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新體驗 好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495b9fe7e13020d89b2c777acd3ddd2c0d64c71a","tid":416331,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"其實帶來的效果如果善用嘅話會好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921cca135858edf884156018d213e85ecb378839","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實帶來的效果如果善用嘅話會好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地話靈魂出竅可以穿牆 甚至有可能睇意識以外嘅野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6c7c768c983e75f817ce0a6031132d58e3634e","tid":416331,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"係叫睡眠癱瘓症"},{"pid":"cb48f02c0dba261ed6d90e34b937533b2007b9de","tid":416331,"uid":83575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:23:46.000Z","msg":"通常因為肉體太攰未起得切身 個腦已經好active醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 休息多d啦"},{"pid":"b0614c78ab5fee93264356f94534160463d1a22e","tid":416331,"uid":9013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:46:43.000Z","msg":"我試過有次係普通嘅鬼壓床...但奇怪嘅係發生之前我發左個短夢，個夢入面我訓係一張單人床上，個空間唔大，但連住一條勁長嘅走廊。<br />\n<br />\n突然，走廊尾果道門無啦啦開左，之後有個人形黑影好快咁行黎我度。我一嚇醒就發生比鬼壓果d現象"},{"pid":"c134c0aac506ea79769a137c396df0a3a19c7624","tid":416331,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，有一排我成日出現呢種情況，初初好驚<br />\n之後有幾次中午訓個時又出現過，出現呢種情況個時，大腦仲諗到野，我就心諗，窗邊咁大太陽我就唔信咁邪，之後就同佢鬥力，慢慢手指可以自由活動，但手腕就郁唔到，但之後好攰<br />\n<br />\n所以而家每次出現呢種情況,都係唔理佢合埋眼，繼續訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你下次試下唔好爭扎 慢慢你會聽到收音機沙沙聲<br />\n人地話個聲冇左之後可在靈魂出竅<br />\n<br />\n利申 而家返工冇晏晝可以試 夜晚又恐怖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我通常個人好攰個排會特別容易鬼壓床  <br />\n所以我都唔太信呢回事   <br />\n不過我每次鬼壓床都一定會有你所講既沙沙聲   <br />\n個人愈想掙扎起身啲沙沙聲就愈會大聲愈刺耳  <br />\n每次意識到鬼壓床之後大約幾秒我就會聽到呢啲聲 <br />\n就confirm到自己唔係發緊夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我慣左就次次都無理到佢  繼續放鬆返個人就會訓返著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無靈魂出竅<br />\n我相信九成九有鬼壓床既人都係身體同精神上太疲勞<br />\n休息多啲啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03881a5390ed1402832d893ae70b403514a4a76","tid":416331,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"我訓晏教到入黑之時個陣<br />\n成日都有呢種徵狀<br />\n所以好多時都唔敢訓晏教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b979ab4a439afc86588bd82cb9d69046ef53b562","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T22:57:57.000Z","msg":"試過夢中夢同鬼壓床同時發生<br />\n一開始鬼壓床 跟著無啦啦個人醒左 咁我以爲就真係醒左 點知過多陣又訓醒多次 個身依然係壓緊 個感覺好正<br />\n<br />\n利申 好多經驗"},{"pid":"b37d79f33ffa1a8a060185e54df3629b15f987a1","tid":416331,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:52:04.000Z","msg":"正氣健康後生仔未試過呢d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b1c4429552e5182c9a44c48c22049582587ac3","tid":416331,"uid":91982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"806147750deed10247e5379e12c3eb06648074aa","tid":416331,"uid":118827,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:27:06.000Z","msg":"鬼你老母壓床<br />\n比鬼(擇)呀"},{"pid":"70145149484a3e70e2f7cd311a89c96a7613ff1e","tid":416331,"uid":22899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"經常性俾鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要收工之後唔覺意恰著咗，夜晚再訓基本上都會俾鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最勁一晚可以壓4，5次<br />\n不過通常播住歌黎訓就會無事"},{"pid":"33b889bd1ca3b156fb707d642c74694ec89910ad","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼你老母壓床<br />\n比鬼(擇)呀</blockquote><br />\n擇你老 而家叫你比鬼揀咩"},{"pid":"7d099f49cecbb6974045311586127a20911930ed","tid":416331,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"淨係試過夢入面知自己發緊夢，想醒但醒唔到，要隔一陣先醒到"},{"pid":"c3a24cd9d591d8d57b0e9f79623fa146170f9f6f","tid":416331,"uid":61888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"俾鬼屌仲恐懼呀"},{"pid":"e34aa2c32b1f4ca666d1d213344cf75df49de383","tid":416331,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，有一排我成日出現呢種情況，初初好驚<br />\n之後有幾次中午訓個時又出現過，出現呢種情況個時，大腦仲諗到野，我就心諗，窗邊咁大太陽我就唔信咁邪，之後就同佢鬥力，慢慢手指可以自由活動，但手腕就郁唔到，但之後好攰<br />\n<br />\n所以而家每次出現呢種情況,都係唔理佢合埋眼，繼續訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你下次試下唔好爭扎 慢慢你會聽到收音機沙沙聲<br />\n人地話個聲冇左之後可在靈魂出竅<br />\n<br />\n利申 而家返工冇晏晝可以試 夜晚又恐怖</blockquote><br />\n真 有雜聲聽到 我聽到球場好多人嘈緊既聲"},{"pid":"2c71b6becabc5534b31b02bb959b269084997805","tid":416331,"uid":76793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:30:57.000Z","msg":"發夢個陣<br />\n開飯 坐係張枱到 見到枱底有個細佬係到 (唔識)<br />\n佢伸手上枱想偷食 比我見到 <br />\n我阻止左佢 之後個人就醒左 好清醒個隻 <br />\n 個身郁唔到同好寒 唔敢開眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6138624c13e5ffb269934e87ceb1b3446b4eedf","tid":416331,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"我係試過個心嚇得勁快，聽到怪聲，醒咗又發覺唔係真係醒咗"},{"pid":"9a9a1932ebd4a461cd0daaf93d77e910f38779dc","tid":416331,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"由細到大成日會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最少試過千幾次 <br />\n基本上果晚有第一次就會成晚keep住有<br />\n一時一晚可以幾十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓之前已經feel到將會比鬼壓<br />\n<br />\n細個會好驚成日掙扎 因為有時會聽到怪聲 <br />\n最驚果2次係聽到有女人係我耳邊尖叫 同埋feel到有野慢慢走上我張床然後捉住我隻腳 嚇到我即刻開哂全屋既燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過大個左少左 同埋理性同自己講唔關鬼怪事 所以無咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5bb7515db95f26afadeb094d573dd43f6951c7","tid":416331,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，有一排我成日出現呢種情況，初初好驚<br />\n之後有幾次中午訓個時又出現過，出現呢種情況個時，大腦仲諗到野，我就心諗，窗邊咁大太陽我就唔信咁邪，之後就同佢鬥力，慢慢手指可以自由活動，但手腕就郁唔到，但之後好攰<br />\n<br />\n所以而家每次出現呢種情況,都係唔理佢合埋眼，繼續訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你下次試下唔好爭扎 慢慢你會聽到收音機沙沙聲<br />\n人地話個聲冇左之後可在靈魂出竅<br />\n<br />\n利申 而家返工冇晏晝可以試 夜晚又恐怖</blockquote><br />\n試過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似situp咁要好用力咁起身 一唔夠力就會彈返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成功左之後望到自己 仲係屋企飛黎飛去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個感覺好真實 不過都係發夢當係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5830f1f1dfc8e2d2e46cb56544ca278a4c1e7e02","tid":416331,"uid":63150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"可能有少少offtopic但分享下<br />\n<br />\n我以前屋企未裝修，牆身唔平，油油表面有陽光就會反光<br />\n<br />\n有一次發夢見最尾一個scene係去左海灘<br />\n之後海灘望出海咪反哂光<br />\n個刻醒左開眼就發覺其實係牆身反光再幻想出黎變夢中場景<br />\n<br />\n者係我訓時隻眼唔係完全合眼，咁我潛意識隻眼望到既野就會加以創造<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自此我就唔會再信呢d野<br />\n例如鬼壓最普通其實係耳嗚之後咩都無<br />\n但其實進化d係可以有其他野<br />\n例如我試過鬼壓時天花有綠光女身影，之後我心講左句&quot;做mud撚野？&quot; 最後有把女聲&quot;無野~~~&quot;<br />\n<br />\n其實諗返都可能係大腦在非清醒下5 官收到訊息而幻想出黎"},{"pid":"792d93ce102694625eebd3ea08e6613997e3bc0c","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係試過夢入面知自己發緊夢，想醒但醒唔到，要隔一陣先醒到</blockquote><br />\n正啊 如果意念再勁就可以控制個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44b7edbcf1014167d3033817c6de43047e02b79","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大成日會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最少試過千幾次 <br />\n基本上果晚有第一次就會成晚keep住有<br />\n一時一晚可以幾十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓之前已經feel到將會比鬼壓<br />\n<br />\n細個會好驚成日掙扎 因為有時會聽到怪聲 <br />\n最驚果2次係聽到有女人係我耳邊尖叫 同埋feel到有野慢慢走上我張床然後捉住我隻腳 嚇到我即刻開哂全屋既燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過大個左少左 同埋理性同自己講唔關鬼怪事 所以無咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa0cd2734c4b6e268c5904ea366e28f7327cd24","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，有一排我成日出現呢種情況，初初好驚<br />\n之後有幾次中午訓個時又出現過，出現呢種情況個時，大腦仲諗到野，我就心諗，窗邊咁大太陽我就唔信咁邪，之後就同佢鬥力，慢慢手指可以自由活動，但手腕就郁唔到，但之後好攰<br />\n<br />\n所以而家每次出現呢種情況,都係唔理佢合埋眼，繼續訓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你下次試下唔好爭扎 慢慢你會聽到收音機沙沙聲<br />\n人地話個聲冇左之後可在靈魂出竅<br />\n<br />\n利申 而家返工冇晏晝可以試 夜晚又恐怖</blockquote><br />\n試過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似situp咁要好用力咁起身 一唔夠力就會彈返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成功左之後望到自己 仲係屋企飛黎飛去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個感覺好真實 不過都係發夢當係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該唔係發夢黎 個個發生都係同一個過程<br />\n好羨慕你啊 我都想體驗下見到自己"},{"pid":"5a29f2fa3be7544060ab0666ea4f21bdb9146d7a","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能有少少offtopic但分享下<br />\n<br />\n我以前屋企未裝修，牆身唔平，油油表面有陽光就會反光<br />\n<br />\n有一次發夢見最尾一個scene係去左海灘<br />\n之後海灘望出海咪反哂光<br />\n個刻醒左開眼就發覺其實係牆身反光再幻想出黎變夢中場景<br />\n<br />\n者係我訓時隻眼唔係完全合眼，咁我潛意識隻眼望到既野就會加以創造<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自此我就唔會再信呢d野<br />\n例如鬼壓最普通其實係耳嗚之後咩都無<br />\n但其實進化d係可以有其他野<br />\n例如我試過鬼壓時天花有綠光女身影，之後我心講左句&quot;做mud撚野？&quot; 最後有把女聲&quot;無野~~~&quot;<br />\n<br />\n其實諗返都可能係大腦在非清醒下5 官收到訊息而幻想出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前面講過樣我都試過，但仲有一種<br />\n有次唔記得發緊咩夢，就完果陣夢入面見到有人係隔離，然後慢慢醒打開眼啊媽真係隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d45eb68158f4146b616ad4e39f5ee86f86a1710","tid":416331,"uid":82717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"最近有晚太夜瞓，果晚連續兩次。之後轉側睡就好好瞓。<br />\n每次都係攰又瞓唔著同埋仰睡先會係咁。係酒店試過，係屋企都試過。"},{"pid":"ae6093d548db0b485b8cd0c6529e17e0be141d64","tid":416331,"uid":54579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"之前聽過有得解釋，當個人太攰，肉體比精神更快進入睡眠狀態，就會有鬼壓床情況出現"},{"pid":"700db2a69d2d670d749ada4cfae0581999e575cb","tid":416331,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過有次係普通嘅鬼壓床...但奇怪嘅係發生之前我發左個短夢，個夢入面我訓係一張單人床上，個空間唔大，但連住一條勁長嘅走廊。<br />\n<br />\n突然，走廊尾果道門無啦啦開左，之後有個人形黑影好快咁行黎我度。我一嚇醒就發生比鬼壓果d現象</blockquote><br />\n我都試過有幻覺，被壓時背景係深淵，隔離有個女人係咁喃喃自語，門口有個男人係咁撞門"},{"pid":"74a51efa171aaf56da04b761ac7055faa6df420f","tid":416331,"uid":75320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r