/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0103cf31ede42f77a98c51e8233cda6d8b37f297","tid":416331,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"郁唔到唔係最驚，講唔到嘢，連叫救命都唔得果下真係驚到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70931416ded126bb2d03615ddb3066a3a32e021b","tid":416331,"uid":36952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/231539_3ccb4dae449331cdae9a2795e794b9b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F231539_3ccb4dae449331cdae9a2795e794b9b0.jpg&h=207b4e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【被鬼壓｜睡眠癱瘓症】<br />\n唔知大家有冇試過，訓訓下教醒咗，眼睇到野，耳聽到聲，但就係無法郁唔到，亦講唔到野，如果係咁，你就係感受緊「被鬼壓」啦！<br />\n<br />\n被鬼壓，又稱睡眠癱瘓症，通常發生喺岩岩訓著，或者就訓醒嘅時候。病發者喺幾分鐘之後就會回復正常，身體逐漸恢復動作，其實絕大多數嘅案例，都係對身體無害，反而係唔好亂諗鬼神之說，嚇親自己，因為其實係兩者並無關連。<br />\n<br />\n其實發生被鬼壓嘅，通常都係年輕人，由壓力﹑作息時間唔規律又或者係訓得太耐所導致。有時做完劇烈運動，吸收大量碳水化合物嘅食物，都會引起低血鉀症而導致被鬼壓。其實只要得閒做下帶氧運動﹑放鬆自己，同埋營造良好嘅睡眠環境，都可以解低「被鬼壓」嘅機會，如果真係經常出現，就需要搵醫生求助啦。<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，放鬆下啦香港人！唔好疑神疑鬼啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n------------------<br />\n◆ 瑜伽入門教室：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/VyHT9G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVyHT9G&d=Iq2FboJiTy84OGc%2Be90xiS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f2a65d45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/VyHT9G</a><br />\n------------------<br />\n◆ 每日分享知識、每月提供課程<br />\n◆ Beginneros網站：<a href=\"https://www.beginneros.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beginneros.com%2F&d=Iq2FboJiTy84OGc%2Be90xiS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c7fdf589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.beginneros.com/</a><br />\n◆ Youtube：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/OEJrGt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FOEJrGt&d=Iq2FboJiTy84OGc%2Be90xiS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=50811a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/OEJrGt</a><br />\n◆ 冷知識投稿：<a href=\"http://goo.gl/zEYS3q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzEYS3q&d=Iq2FboJiTy84OGc%2Be90xiS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=21838267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://goo.gl/zEYS3q</a>"},{"pid":"9bf4ec00de223e1c813d939c4c8d230b8c52c796","tid":416331,"uid":49799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:20:29.000Z","msg":"初初試靈魂出體真係幾驚，但試多幾次又覺得好撚high <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左訓着左先會俾鬼澤，訓着前都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我平時好難訓得着，試過不斷暗示自己要靈魂出體，然後觀察自己訓着<br />\n真係好神奇咁有一刻個身體突然熄左掣，但個腦仲係清醒，之後就可以靈魂出體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e72491289bbe10c841bc87d888dd98a19fccdd7","tid":416331,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"大概有五次<br />\n身體唔係郁唔到，係出盡力都淨係郁得嗰幾毫米，眼光光，出唔到聲。。。"},{"pid":"2d95f060ce59f653cf2e4a7e086bf8f006b00122","tid":416331,"uid":133571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"試過好多次，多數訓晏教果時會。<br />\n無耐前喺屋企比鬼壓，見到有個人入左屋企另一間房，但屋企無呢個人。<br />\n有時會有幻聽好嘈好多人講野，會有窒息同起雞皮。<br />\n不過好清楚係正常現象"},{"pid":"dce91d14fd3d4b18370d7f6e3e7c0bd52ab44b2e","tid":416331,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"有 <br />\n訓訓下聽到好多人聲 又有人叫我<br />\n但我應唔到佢 又開唔到眼<br />\n一開到眼嗰陣突然無哂聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57a9bd96b4d6984c3f4301b3a32d7c6a4dabec6","tid":416331,"uid":150013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"我有一次直情係成個人好似被對無形手㩒住膊頭，跟住好明顯拖我起身。"},{"pid":"f17bfe8a7fa979febc8cf28d12851704ca09c720","tid":416331,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"有冇機會係被外星人捉去做完秘密實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9ab6cf1bf64e7def71cb209c1d5f0f82ec00f9","tid":416331,"uid":53397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:55:47.000Z","msg":"發夢一次<br />\n好似比野縛住<br />\n跟住同自己講醒呀！起身呀<br />\n掙扎左陣 先起倒身 個人出緊汗"},{"pid":"1247b44d6f26906a76cdd6fcda13d9c22d5a93ef","tid":416331,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"記得響高登睇過個post<br />\n講到只要識活用比鬼壓<br />\n可以延伸到控制夢境 靈魂出竅 上埋宇宙/其他世界/撞外星人 都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要好多人討論"},{"pid":"b2e1cd741df6c4cccbf050d395df27f991859c3c","tid":416331,"uid":142697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"細個個陣成日訓訓下突然抖唔到氣 野都講唔到 <br />\n最長個次持續左兩分鐘 feel到就頂唔住就抖得返 <br />\n勁驚自己會窒息死 但大左又冇再試過"},{"pid":"06d2bfe765dc02e7421979c350ccf16da6b8d461","tid":416331,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個個陣成日訓訓下突然抖唔到氣 野都講唔到 <br />\n最長個次持續左兩分鐘 feel到就頂唔住就抖得返 <br />\n勁驚自己會窒息死 但大左又冇再試過</blockquote><br />\n睡眠窒息症？ 同睡眠癱瘓症係兩會事嚟"},{"pid":"b79e87e4d629abb4578dff748ca235c2b379ce55","tid":416331,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我好想試</blockquote><br />\n我唔想再試"},{"pid":"cd096e18741b3f987cecc977a135e3e8bc6d2edc","tid":416331,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能有少少offtopic但分享下<br />\n<br />\n我以前屋企未裝修，牆身唔平，油油表面有陽光就會反光<br />\n<br />\n有一次發夢見最尾一個scene係去左海灘<br />\n之後海灘望出海咪反哂光<br />\n個刻醒左開眼就發覺其實係牆身反光再幻想出黎變夢中場景<br />\n<br />\n者係我訓時隻眼唔係完全合眼，咁我潛意識隻眼望到既野就會加以創造<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自此我就唔會再信呢d野<br />\n例如鬼壓最普通其實係耳嗚之後咩都無<br />\n但其實進化d係可以有其他野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如我試過鬼壓時天花有綠光女身影，之後我心講左句&quot;做mud撚野？&quot; 最後有把女聲&quot;無野~~~&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n其實諗返都可能係大腦在非清醒下5 官收到訊息而幻想出黎</blockquote><br />\n紅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe9dab159158ddc2c203fee34b58dfb526ac369","tid":416331,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"抖唔到氣 耳鳴係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}